b'Another demonstration last night that this Fiorentina side is rarely dull. Two makeshift defences produced the anticipated goal feast. Saponara sublime, Duncan diligent and Dusan deadly despite expert \xe2\x80\x9ctreatment\xe2\x80\x9d from Kjaer. Milan showed character, too, in adversity.'

b"Gabbia starting was confirmation. For what it's worth I'm a Gabbia fan but he was skinned by Vlahovic yesterday.

Kj\xc3\xa6r on the other hand showed the best way to mark Dusan was to stay on him, don't give him space.

The moment Dusan was isolated with Gabbia, we saw the outcome."
